Shruthi-1, a better digital/analog hybrid MIDI monosynth.

Copyright 2010 Olivier Gillet (ol.gillet@gmail.com)

# The firmware is released under a GPL3.0 license. It includes external code from the following sources:
- Parts of the Arduino library (real time clock and timed delay for software serial).
- Parts of M J Oldfield's makefile for Arduino project.
- A reimplementation of the formant synthesis algorithm used in Peter Knight's Cantarino speech synthesizer.

# The PCB layouts and schematics (in /hardware/shruti/hardware_design) are released under a Creative Commons cc-by-nc-sa 3.0 license.
